#: ../../manual/getting_started/configuration/hardware.rst:7
msgid "Displays"
msgstr "显示器"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/configuration/hardware.rst:9
msgid ""
"A full HD display or higher is recommended. Multi-monitor setups are supported, and "
"workspaces can be configured to span multiple monitors."
msgstr ""
"推荐使用全高清或更高配置的显示器。支持多显示器，可以配置工作区来扩展到多个显示器。"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/configuration/hardware.rst:14
msgid "Example of Blender's multi-monitor support."
msgstr "Blender多显示器支持示例。"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/configuration/hardware.rst:18
msgid "Input Devices"
msgstr "输入设备"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/configuration/hardware.rst:20
msgid "Blender supports various types of input devices:"
msgstr "Blender支持各种类型的输入设备:"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/configuration/hardware.rst:22
msgid ""
"Keyboard (recommended: keyboard with numeric keypad, English layout works best)"
msgstr "键盘 (推荐: 有数字键区的键盘，最好是英文布局)"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/configuration/hardware.rst:23
msgid "Mouse (recommended: three button mouse with scroll wheel)"
msgstr "鼠标 (推荐: 带滚轮的三键鼠标)"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/configuration/hardware.rst:24
msgid "NDOF Device (also known as *3D Mouse*)"
msgstr "NDOF 设备 (也称作 *3D鼠标*)"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/configuration/hardware.rst:25
#: ../../manual/getting_started/configuration/hardware.rst:89
msgid "Graphic Tablet"
msgstr "绘图板"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/configuration/hardware.rst:29
msgid ""
"If you are missing an input device such as a mouse or numpad Blender can change "
"its :doc:`keymap </interface/keymap/blender_default>` to emulate these devices. "
"Settings to enable this can be found in the :doc:`Input Preferences </editors/"
"preferences/input>`."
msgstr ""
"如果缺少鼠标或数字键区的输入设备，可以配置Blender :doc:`键区映射 </interface/keymap/"
"blender_default>` 里来模拟。查看 :doc:`输入设置 </editors/preferences/input>` 打开此"
"功能。"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/configuration/hardware.rst:35
msgid "Mouse"
msgstr "鼠标"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/configuration/hardware.rst:38
msgid "Mouse Button Emulation"
msgstr "鼠标按键模拟"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/configuration/hardware.rst:40
msgid ""
"If you do not have a 3 button mouse, you will need to emulate it by checking the "
"option in the :doc:`Preferences </editors/preferences/input>`."
msgstr ""
"如果没有三键鼠标，你需要在 :doc:`用户设置 </editors/preferences/input>` 勾选模拟三键"
"鼠标的选项。"

